item.title: Show HN：AI工具箱 - 免费的小型Web实用程序集合
item.description:
我构建了AI Toolbox，这是一个轻巧的免费Web实用程序集合，用于日常使用。这是一个从业余爱好开始的附带项目，我在这里分享它是为了获得反馈。 built it: I wanted a simple, minimal set of tools that are fast, accessible, and don’t require setting up big dashboards or accounts.I’d love feedback on:Which tools you find useful (or useless)What’s missing that you’d like to see in a toolbox like thisUX, performance, and privacy expectationsIt’s completely free to use, and I’m happy to answer questions about the tech stack, roadmap, or design选择。
